flowchart TD
    Start([Developer Arrives]) --> Sync[Git pull origin main]
    Sync --> CheckStatus[swaif status]
    
    CheckStatus --> ReviewDashboard{Review<br/>Dashboard}
    ReviewDashboard --> CheckPending{Pending<br/>Approvals?}
    
    CheckPending -->|Yes| ReviewGates[Review gate requests]
    ReviewGates --> ApproveGates[Approve or reject gates]
    ApproveGates --> CheckPending
    
    CheckPending -->|No| ListTasks[swaif tasks list<br/>--assigned-to=me]
    
    ListTasks --> SelectTask{Tasks<br/>Available?}
    
    SelectTask -->|No tasks| PairProgramming[Offer to help teammates]
    PairProgramming --> Coffee[Take break ‚òï]
    Coffee --> CheckStatus
    
    SelectTask -->|Tasks ready| ChooseTask[Select highest priority]
    ChooseTask --> AssessTask{Assess<br/>Task Type}
    
    AssessTask -->|Routine<br/>Low Risk| CopilotFlow[Run in Copilot Mode]
    AssessTask -->|Novel<br/>Medium Risk| HumanFlow[Run in Human Mode]
    AssessTask -->|Critical<br/>High Risk| ChallengerFlow[Run in Challenger Mode]
    
    %% Copilot Mode Flow
    CopilotFlow --> StartCopilot[swaif implement<br/>--task=T-XXX<br/>--mode=copilot]
    StartCopilot --> CopilotExecute[ü§ñ AI executes fully]
    CopilotExecute --> CopilotTests[AI writes tests]
    CopilotTests --> CopilotCode[AI writes code]
    CopilotCode --> CopilotDocs[AI updates docs]
    CopilotDocs --> CopilotCommit[AI commits with traceability]
    CopilotCommit --> CopilotCI{CI<br/>Passes?}
    CopilotCI -->|Yes| TaskComplete[Task marked complete ‚úì]
    CopilotCI -->|No| ReviewFailure[Review CI errors]
    ReviewFailure --> FixIssue{Can<br/>Auto-fix?}
    FixIssue -->|Yes| CopilotExecute
    FixIssue -->|No| ManualDebug[Debug manually]
    ManualDebug --> CopilotCode
    
    %% Human Mode Flow
    HumanFlow --> StartHuman[swaif implement<br/>--task=T-YYY<br/>--mode=human]
    StartHuman --> HumanProposal[AI proposes plan]
    HumanProposal --> ReviewPlan{Review<br/>Plan OK?}
    ReviewPlan -->|No| ModifyPlan[Request changes]
    ModifyPlan --> HumanProposal
    ReviewPlan -->|Yes| ApprovePlan[Approve plan]
    ApprovePlan --> HumanTests[AI writes tests]
    HumanTests --> ReviewTests{Review<br/>Tests OK?}
    ReviewTests -->|No| ModifyTests[Request changes]
    ModifyTests --> HumanTests
    ReviewTests -->|Yes| ApproveTests[Approve tests]
    ApproveTests --> HumanCode[AI implements code]
    HumanCode --> ReviewCode{Review<br/>Code OK?}
    ReviewCode -->|No| ModifyCode[Request changes]
    ModifyCode --> HumanCode
    ReviewCode -->|Yes| ApproveCommit[Approve commit]
    ApproveCommit --> HumanCI{CI<br/>Passes?}
    HumanCI -->|Yes| TaskComplete
    HumanCI -->|No| ReviewCode
    
    %% Challenger Mode Flow
    ChallengerFlow --> StartChallenger[swaif implement<br/>--task=T-ZZZ<br/>--mode=challenger]
    StartChallenger --> ProposerImpl[‚öîÔ∏è Proposer AI:<br/>Implement solution]
    ProposerImpl --> ChallengerAttack[‚öîÔ∏è Challenger AI:<br/>Attack design]
    ChallengerAttack --> ProposerDefend[‚öîÔ∏è Proposer AI:<br/>Defend & revise]
    ProposerDefend --> ReviewDebate{Review<br/>Debate}
    ReviewDebate --> Arbitrate{Human<br/>Decision}
    Arbitrate -->|Approve| FinalizeChallenger[Finalize implementation]
    Arbitrate -->|Request revision| ProposerImpl
    Arbitrate -->|Reject approach| StartChallenger
    FinalizeChallenger --> ChallengerTests[Write comprehensive tests]
    ChallengerTests --> ChallengerCode[Implement with safeguards]
    ChallengerCode --> ChallengerCI{CI +<br/>Security<br/>Scan Pass?}
    ChallengerCI -->|Yes| TaskComplete
    ChallengerCI -->|No| ReviewDebate
    
    %% Post-Task Activities
    TaskComplete --> UpdateStatus[swaif status update]
    UpdateStatus --> CheckBlocked{Other Tasks<br/>Unblocked?}
    CheckBlocked -->|Yes| NotifyTeam[Notify team]
    NotifyTeam --> CheckBlocked
    CheckBlocked -->|No| PushChanges[git push origin main]
    
    PushChanges --> IntegrationCheck{Integration<br/>OK?}
    IntegrationCheck -->|No| ResolveConflicts[Resolve conflicts]
    ResolveConflicts --> PushChanges
    IntegrationCheck -->|Yes| CheckTime{Time for<br/>Another Task?}
    
    CheckTime -->|Yes, < 2 hours left| QuickTask[Find short task<br/><2 hours]
    QuickTask --> SelectTask
    
    CheckTime -->|Yes, > 2 hours left| ListTasks
    
    CheckTime -->|No, end of day| Standup[swaif standup generate]
    Standup --> StandupReport[Review generated report]
    StandupReport --> CheckStageGate{Current Stage<br/>Complete?}
    
    CheckStageGate -->|Yes| RequestGateApproval[swaif gate review STAGE]
    RequestGateApproval --> PreparePresentation[Prepare gate artifacts]
    PreparePresentation --> CheckStageGate
    
    CheckStageGate -->|No| UpdateTeam[Post standup to team chat]
    UpdateTeam --> ReviewMetrics[Check project metrics]
    ReviewMetrics --> PlanTomorrow[Plan tomorrow's work]
    PlanTomorrow --> EndDay([Log off üè†])
    
    %% Side flows
    CheckStatus -.->|Blocked issue found| InvestigateBlocker[Investigate blocker]
    InvestigateBlocker -.-> UnblockTask[swaif tasks unblock]
    UnblockTask -.-> CheckStatus
    
    TaskComplete -.->|Coverage < 90%| AddTests[Add more tests]
    AddTests -.-> TaskComplete
    
